{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b06389421e","title":"给复旦大学全校教职员工大会的一封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"39ad49f7f1","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":3,"articleId":"b06389421e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4ad1aa8056","name":"复旦大学"},{"id":"9d913d16f5","name":"孙大雨"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4eb2b4952c","type":"title","text":"给复旦大学全校教职员工大会的一封信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b06389421e"},{"id":"f398d64690","type":"authors","text":"复旦大学孙大雨","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b06389421e"},{"id":"c276259bbc","type":"paragraph","text":"编者按：7月3日复旦大学召开全校教职员工大会，会上对右派分子孙大雨进行揭发和批判，孙大雨托病没有出席，寄了一封信给大会。全文如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b06389421e"},{"id":"5f667f5bb5","type":"paragraph","text":"我有病请假，混身神经痛，不能来参加会议。我对于上月7日我在全校座谈会上的发言，并无变动。上月17日我写了一篇东西驳斥徐常太《新闻(日报)》、《解放(日报)》两张报纸和漆琪生、章靳以等，送各报发表。他们不敢发表出来，加以封锁，却将大量对于我的歪曲、毁谤、造谣、污蔑发表出来。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b06389421e"},{"id":"2931398d16","type":"paragraph","text":"我认为章伯钧、史良、章乃器、储安平是反革命分子，在上海方面，鲁莽和徐仲年是反革命分子。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b06389421e"},{"id":"671e314de0","type":"paragraph","text":" 1957年7月3日孙大雨","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b06389421e"},{"id":"0e20dd5f59","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《批判右派思想言论选辑之一：毒草集》,复旦大学校刊编辑室，1957年8月。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b06389421e"}],"page":{"id":"cd2268b5f0","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b06389421e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}